features: SWIGG PACIFIERS: A favorite for both moms and babies, the SWIGG baby pacifier is crafted with safety in mind. The Swigg flower design pacifier baby soother is made of 100% highest food grade silicone and is tested to meet ASTM safety standards. It is BPA Free, Latex Free Petroleum Free, Lead Free & Phthalates Free.

PACIFIER & TEETHER: The 2 in 1 design is pacifier & teether is soothing & comfortable and gently mimics breastfeeding for natural palette development ,the teether will soothe your baby's gums & allows your child to self-soothe by exercising their instinctive sucking instinct in the most natural way possible, by mimicking both the shape and soft materials of mothers’ breasts.
PROMOTES HEALTHY ORAL DEVELOPMENT: The pacifier's nipple is shaped and designed perfectly to stay in your baby's mouth and will enable healthy oral/palette development.

𝗜𝗡𝗖𝗟𝗨𝗗𝗘𝗦 𝟮 𝗣𝗔𝗖𝗜𝗙𝗜𝗘𝗥𝗦: GORGEOUS FLOWER DESIGN & COLORS: Are you looking to impress with the best? We know how important it is to dress your infants & babies in style and luxury. Enjoy this beautiful flower pacifier soother designed by SWIGG & choose your favorite colors to beautify your princess, crafted with SAFETY in mind! Each purchase includes 2 premium baby pacifiers in a variety of beautiful colors and tones which are distinctively SWIGG.
LARGE BREATHING HOLES: Safety is our #1 priority! Unlike other pacifiers, the SWIGG Pacifier is designed with 2 large breathing holes for added safety & with a security handle.

𝗖𝗔𝗥𝗘 𝗜𝗡𝗦𝗧𝗥𝗨𝗖𝗧𝗜𝗢𝗡𝗦: DURABLE & EASY TO CLEAN: The one-piece design makes the pacifier easy to clean and of course safer! CARE INSTRUCTIONS: Sterilize each pacifier before use by pouring boiling water over it, squeeze any remaining water out, and let dry.Do not use a pacifier that shows changes in color or irregularities. We recommend a replacement every 4-6 weeks for both safety and hygienic reasons.
